the sentence.

39
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:26,500
Please sit down or you can pop it on the
end

40
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:32,360
But and this is a super important if if
you put it at the end you've got to add a
little comma right before it

41
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:37,720
So it's sit down, please. It seems like a
tiny detail, but trust me. It makes all
the difference

42
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:45,700
Okay, fantastic. So you know how to tell
people what to do, but what about telling
them what not to do?

43
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:48,240
