45
00:02:53,600 --> 00:03:01,880
The secret weapon for this command is one
simple powerful word. Are you ready? It's
don't.

46
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:08,640
And guess what? The rule here is just as
easy as before. You literally just put
don't at the

47
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:12,880
very beginning of the sentence right
before that same base verb we've been
using. That's

