00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:17,040
That's it. You're done. And you can see,
this works for everything.

49
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,360
In the hallway at school, don't run.

50
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,960
In the movie theater, don't use your cell
phone here.

51
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:24,920
And yeah, of course it works perfectly
with the B-verb too.

52
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:27,920
In the library, a sign might say, don't be
noisy.

53
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:31,960
And what does your teacher always say?
Don't be late. See?

54
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,320
One simple rule covers them all.

55
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:36,720
Alright, enough with now giving orders and
telling people what to do.

56
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:38,560
I mean, that's not always fun, right?

57
