58
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:45,120
For that, we need the ultimate team-up
phrase.

59
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:50,160
So to invite someone to join in on the
fun, the magic word is let's.

60
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:53,760
It's really just a short, cool way of
